        "BoR Articles I (Scope of Enterprise) — undefined",
        "BoR Articles II (Prohibited Activities) — undefined",
        "BoR Articles III (Core Identity) — undefined",
        "BoR Articles IV (Human Authority Reservation) — undefined",
        "BoR Articles V (Amendment Protocol) — undefined",
        "BoR Articles VI (Interpretation Rules) — undefined",
        "MSP - Relationship to the Bill of Rights (strict subordination of MSP to BoR)"
